      "raw_text": "Judge Huneke today refused to\npass on the constitutionality OF\nthe employers liability act, hold\ning that it properly comes under\nJurisdiction of federal courts. The\ncase came up in the suit of Jap\nlaborer to recover $4,000 from the\nGreat Northern for the loss of two\nthumbs. The constitutionality OF\nthe act was challenged before the\ntrial proceeded."
    }
